imdb.plot outline: The Red Bull Cliff Diving World Series follows traditional high diving thrills and spills with raw, gasp-inducing locations that push the definition of 'cliff' as far as it will go. We'll meet a group of daredevil divers that put their lives on the line to feel the rush of jumping of cliffs, buildings and anything with a stretch of water beneath.
